title: The Veni Station orbiting Mnemosyne
description: Private Yacht. The Even Odds has a golden hull and advanced ion engines. It is equipped with a single luxury suite and defensive force shield.

title: Stellar Pathfinder
description: Research Spaceship. The Stellar Pathfinder has an aerodyne hull and inefficient sublight engines. It is equipped with an advanced sensor system and defensive force shield.

title: Flame of Uryuon
description: The Harrier has a well-armored hull and long-range fusion engines with automatic repair systems. It is equipped with point-defense lasers and armed with rapid-fire railguns.

title: The Sari Terraforming Complex on New Theia
description: Exploration Spaceship. The Yukon has a salvaged hull and an inefficient FTL drive which requires repairs after every run. It is equipped with a planetary sensor system and defensive laser cannon.

title: The Desert Moon of Leko
description: Cargo Spaceship. The Gloni Carrier has an ellipsoid hull and advanced sublight engines. It is equipped with a large detachable cargo container and landing shuttle.

title: The Wreckage of Bari Station orbiting 2250 Dou Xiu VI
description: The Citadel of Mone has a needle-like primary hull welded to twin spherical secondary hulls. It is equipped with a stealth system and armed with particle accelerators and autonomous attack drones.

title: The Volcanic Continent of 7597 Jiao Xiu IV
description: The John Glenn has an elegant hull and an advanced FTL drive. It is equipped with a planetary sensor system and landing shuttle.

title: The Hollow World of Lycia
description: e Spectral Shift has an aerodyne hull with large observation windows. It is equipped with autonomous sensor probes and a landing shuttle.
